structure.name: UBX-NAV-PL
structure.description: This message provides protection level (PL) values per protection level state (e.g. position ECEF X/Y/Z) and w.r.t. the given target misleading information risk (TMIR) per coordinate axis. Target misleading information risk is expressed as X [%MI/epoch] (read: X% probability of having an MI per epoch). Misleading information (MI) occurs when the Protection Level value is smaller than the true position error.
